title: 1975–76 Hibernian F.C. season
text: During the 1975–76 season <a href="Hibernian%20F.C.">Hibernian</a>, a <a href="association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Edinburgh">Edinburgh</a>, came third out of 10 clubs in the <a href="Scottish%20Premier%20Division">Scottish Premier Division</a> and reached the fourth round of the <a href="Scottish%20Cup">Scottish Cup</a>.
